{"tid":628260,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局再入市 買入30.38億港元","createTime":"2018-04-13T16:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T17:19:13.000Z","uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ad6b37b63972e915ec267e53e348359c88c0fdf3","tid":628260,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"金融管理局在港匯觸及7.85後，再次於今晚11時出手，買入30.38億港元。這是自昨晚出手買入8.16億港元，及在今早清晨再度入市承接港元沽盤，買入24.42億元，再一次出手。由昨晚至今，累計3次出手，金管局前後購入62.96億港元。<br />\n<br />\n在金管局多次接入港元沽盤後，銀行體系結餘將由約1800億元，跌至下周二的1734.82億元。<br />\n<br />\n咁買法玩得幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b96881074866c10b9e84d0029cab2d88d317883","tid":628260,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:03:08.000Z","msg":"幫hkma 齊換美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867a0f595515ce794fe18c508eca007a5c48500f","tid":628260,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b96881074866c10b9e84d0029cab2d88d317883","tid":628260,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:03:08.000Z","msg":"幫hkma 齊換美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做到野"},{"pid":"71702da1f260dc1d191f9f3cf101bd13b415f8b5","tid":628260,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167222ceba25253aca6dc8c7924ef978ccc41e78","tid":628260,"uid":99493,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:50:52.000Z","msg":"兩日就60億<br />\n<br />\n一個月一千億<br />\n<br />\n今次仆街了"},{"pid":"d6201fccac7dcf05010b0f848fa3fd3308b8da13","tid":628260,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"167222ceba25